high_descs: Go forward to sink, turn right, go to counter with lettuce and red apple on it.
Pick up red apple, located to the left of the lettuce.
Turn around, go to sink, turn right to face sink
Place apple in sink, in front and between spatula and left side potato.  Turn water on, turn water off.  Pick up apple.
Place apple on table slightly in front and to the right of the apple already on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash an apple and put it on a table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the sink, turn right and head to the apple on the counter.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the dining table on the left.
Put the apple on the dining table, in front of and to the right of the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned apple on a dining table.

high_descs: Move forward to the sink. turn right, move to the apple on the counter.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around, bring the apple to the sink on the right.
Wash the apple with water in the sink.
Turn around with the cleaned apple, move to the table on the left.
Put the apple on the table in front of the other apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned apple on the table.
